      <br><br>
      <p style="margin:4px 20px 18px 20px;width:640px">
        We're so glad that your shipment was delivered on <span class="il">{{shipment.delivered_date}}</span>. If you want to have a look at your final invoice, <a href="{{ENV.URLS_PARCEL}}/shipRequests/history">Click Here</a>.
