      <p style="margin:4px 20px 18px 20px;width:640px">
        Your shipment Cancelled. ShipmentId is<span class="il">{{shipment.id}}</span>.
        <br>
        <br>
      </p> </td>
  </tr>
{{else if PAYMENT_DELAY}}
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" style="width:640px">
      <p style="font:18px Arial,sans-serif;color:#cc6600;margin:15px 20px 0 20px">Hi {{customer.first_name}},</p> <br>
      <p style="margin:4px 20px 18px 20px;width:640px">
        This is to inform you that you haven't made payment for the order <span class="il">{{shipment.id}}</span> after creating the Ship Request for the same.
        <br><br>
        You'd have to pay in the next 2 days or since then you'll have to pay an additional fee of Rs.<span class="il">{{shipment.payment_delay_charge}}</span>/- per day.
      </p> </td>
  </tr>
{{else if PAYMENT_DELAY_EXCEEDED}}
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2" style="width:640px">
      <p style="font:18px Arial,sans-serif;color:#cc6600;margin:15px 20px 0 20px">Hi {{customer.first_name}},</p> <br>
      <p style="margin:4px 20px 18px 20px;width:640px">
        This is to inform you that you have exceeded the <span class="il">{{shipment.payment_delay_limit}}</span> days of grace period you had for making payment for the order <span class="il">{{shipment.id}}</span>.
        <br><br>
